{"type": "article", "id": 16818, "title": "“XYZ 粘钩”", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-30T07:20:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115211sTO7ydvoBaeJtG9j.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t挂钩不仅仅是挂衣服或者袋子，也可以固定小物品。这些来自韩国 250 设计工作室的粘钩，就将普通的挂钩改成了“叉”型，且横竖皆可。因为硅胶材料拥有弹性，可以将小物件卡在中间，相当于一个放置小物品的地方。粘合胶垫经过水冲洗后可以重复使用，耐磨防水，适合厨房和浴室。这款挂钩有 5 种颜色，<a href=\"http://storefarm.naver.com/250/products/295444778\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144118I3WFmwH9koUzViMs.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"577\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70537897\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144119gM7CKR9LPTrsU5lO.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"577\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70537897\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261441192CuHSrIjZVUYewsX.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144119YQO9kWxGsbMTJXg0.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}